  <meetYourRep><![CDATA[<p><strong>Transfers</strong></p>
<p>All guests are booked onto the <strong>Whistler Connection</strong> shuttle service. With 30 years of experiences, they will get you and other ski enthusiast swiftly and safely to Whistler via the Sea to Sky highway. The journey is approximately 2 hours and if required, time for a quick comfort break enroute, just speak to your friendly driver to help or answer any questions you might have. Your return transfer time will be communicated to you a few days before departure by your rep. </p>
<p>Private transfers available at additional cost, please ask at time of booking. </p>
<p><strong>Rep Service </strong></p>
<p>Inghams operate a part time rep serviced based in resort. Please be aware we do not have a rep to meet you at the airport. Please follow instruction on your transfer documents as to where to meet your transfer driver. </p>
<p>Once in resort, your rep aims to contact you by WhatsApp within 24 hours of your arrival and will be on hand for any questions you may have that haven't been answered in your detailed welcome pack available both on the 'My Booking' section of our website and sent to you before you travel. Please be sure to give us your contact details before you travel. </p>]]></meetYourRep>
