    "subTabDescription": "<p><strong>Lift Tickets</strong></p>\n<h4><strong>Prices increase the closer you get to your departure date. Pre-book your lift ticket early to secure the lowest price. Prices will be considerably more expensive in resort.</strong></h4>\n<p> </p>\n<div style=\"-ms-overflow-x: auto;\">\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"width: 647px; height: 66px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 42px;\">\n<th style=\"width: 290px; height: 41px; text-align: center;\"><strong>Whistler Blackcomb Lift Ticket</strong></th>\n<th style=\"width: 143px; height: 41px; text-align: center;\"><strong>Child<br />5 - 12 years</strong></th>\n<th style=\"width: 147px; text-align: center; height: 41px;\"><strong>Teen<br />13 - 18 years</strong></th>\n<th style=\"width: 158px; height: 41px; text-align: center;\"><strong>Adult<br />19 - 64 years</strong></th>\n<th style=\"width: 143px; text-align: center; height: 41px;\"><strong>Senior<br />65+ years</strong></th>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"width: 290px; height: 20px;\">6 Day Lift Ticket - Whole Area</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"width: 143px; height: 20px;\">From £451</td>\n<td style=\"width: 147px; text-align: center; height: 20px;\">From £766</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"width: 158px; height: 20px;\">From £901</td>\n<td style=\"width: 143px; text-align: center; height: 20px;\">From £809</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4><strong> </strong><strong>Lift ticket information</strong></h4>\n</div>\n<ul>\n<li>Children (0-5yrs) can pick up a free lift pass locally</li>\n<li>Your lift ticket allows for a certain number of non-ski days with the following example grace periods:\n<ul>\n<li>3-4 day tickets have 2 grace days and can be used within a period of 5-6 days respectively</li>\n<li>5-7 day tickets have 3 grace days and can be used within a period of 8-10 days respectively</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Pre-booked lift tickets can be picked up in resort by visiting a lift ticket desk. These can be found next to the lift stations at the foot of both Whistler Mountain and Blackcomb Mountain. You will require photo ID and your confirmation number which will be sent to you after booking.</p>\n<p><strong>Prices and supplements are correct at time of publishing but may vary up or down; correct prices will be advised at the time of booking.</strong></p>"
